  "title": "3D Designer/Draughtman",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>· Develop conceptual design from guidelines given from\nclients or from scratch;</p><p>· Design documentation, preparing of material boards and\nartwork for production;</p><p>· Provide 3D drawings for submission</p><p>· Involve in project development, supervision and\ncoordination</p><p>· Liaising with clients & suppliers</p><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>· Minimum 3 years’ experience in product industrial design /\ncommercial / interior / exhibition</p><p>· Possess a diploma / degree in design or equivalent</p><p>· Proficiency in 3D studio max, Vray renderer, Sketch up\nPro, Autocad, Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator</p><p>· Good presentation skills & ability to manage clients\n& suppliers</p><p>· Highly initiative with responsible working attitude</p><p>· Able to work under pressure / tight deadline &\nindependently</p>",
